Beng<br />\n唯一hkie認  所以行內好睇<br />\n如果想入consultant firm一般bsc envr識唔夠多technicial野 所以好難入  所以我就入左mc<br />\n<br />\n你要研究清楚係咪想做envr 方向<br />\n依行好細  我因為eo duty太刻板所以轉safety,始終對人既野有意思d同career prospects好"},{"pid":"6787f9ee130b625fab403aea0ffe4f0099d9b4b1","tid":278612,"uid":64496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T23:31:14.000Z","msg":"冇撚用，讀postgrad悔終生"},{"pid":"802d5a3cd2dbe8b60ade114a2d34c6391e5aa233","tid":278612,"uid":68802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T23:36:13.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n讀taught master係俾錢買紙<br />\n收d人低質到連m=萬都講得出嘅engineer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}